            <description>
&lt;p&gt;WS-Federation is adopting SAML 2.0 metadata when it releases WS-Federation 1.2.  OpenSSO uses WS-Fed 1.1 metadata which is now deprecated.  Expect to see an openSSO release soon that will adopt WS-Fed 1.2&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;h4&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://identity-des.com/2008/10/28/harmonized-federation-metadata-for-ws-federation-and-saml&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://identity-des.com/2008/10/28/harmonized-federation-metadata-for-ws-federation-and-saml&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

