&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s a video about mySQL ndbcluster presented during google tech talk. The presenter is Stewart Smith who works for MySQL AB as a software engineer working on MySQL Cluster. He is an active member of the free and open source software community, especially in Australia.&lt;br/&gt;
