    <category>rant</category>
            <description>while the entire industry harps on &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.google.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;google&lt;/a&gt; and it&apos;s &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.google.ca/search?oi=stock&amp;q=stocks:GOOG&amp;prev=/search%3Fq%3DGOOG%26hl%3Den%26lr%3D&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;stock price&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://myweb2.search.yahoo.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Yahoo&lt;/a&gt; is way ahead of the game with &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.oreillynet.com/pub/a/oreilly/tim/news/2005/09/30/what-is-web-20.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;web 2.0&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;a href=&quot;http://myweb2.search.yahoo.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;check them out&lt;/a&gt; and decide for yourselves. Comments welcome!!

